song.title: One Must Fall 2012-12-12
song.info:
Happy 2012-12-12 12:12:12:12121212! I hope ya all have a great day and celebrate this date. Next one won't appear until a few 100 years :)
This is a remix of Kenny Chow's One Must Fall 2097 - Title Screen. My good friend PsyDOS already made a superb remix of this, but here's my take on it, I hope you all like it.
